parameters:
It's been over a month since I last heard from
Esuka. Despite desperate searches, there's not a
single trace of her.

Damn it! Where on earth is she... Please, I beg
you, contact me...!

A message from headquarters...⁉ Could it be that
they've found Esuka...⁉

Shuu, about the auction we discussed, we've
received several videos from the infiltrated
resistance. It's hard to say, but we've also
spotted a person who appears to be Esuka in them.
It's painful, but if it's true, as a resistance...

We must consider our response. I'll send you the
footage, so I want you to confirm if it's her.

What do you mean, Esuka...? If that's the case,
why aren't we immediately going to rescue her...!

While suppressing his frustration, he plays the
video that was sent to him.

He must have been tortured, his face was terribly
damaged, but there was no mistaking that face I
had seen over and over again.

So...someone...! Please, someone buy me! I beg
you! I'll do...I'll do anything...!

Please! I beg you! If things stay like this, I'll
be killed...! Help me... Help me, Shuu...

Come on, anyone there⁉ The cyborg woman from the
Resistance! Now for just 500 yen! Cheaper than any
toy around!
Even in this state, she's fully conscious, see!

How about it, she screams quite nicely, doesn't
she? No...? Then how about for 300 yen!
Come on! You should beg too!

P-Please...! I beg you! Someone! Someone help me!
Help me!

Beg and grovel to the customers more! You've seen
what happens to the ones who don't sell, haven't
you...?

E-Everyone, I'll do anything...! My body may be
broken, but my breasts are still soft, and I can
still use my mouth~?

That's right! That's right! Can she properly be
used as a sex toy!?

Come on! Think of this as your master, and show us
your service!

What's this, what's this? Your master won't be
satisfied with just that!

Insults were hurled at Esuka, who inadvertently
let go of the rod when an electric current was
sent through her mouth.
Do you even want to do this!

Wait... Please let me do it one more time, just
once more...!
Ignoring Esuka's plea, boos echoed from the crowd.

Too bad, then the unsold one will be executed as
usual!

No! Stop! Why! Why won't anyone buy me! I'll do
anything, absolutely anything!
No one wants someone like you.
Now, everyone, don't take your eyes off!

Esuka lost her words to the jeers from the
audience. She showed a moment of agitation, but
soon murmured as if she had given up on
everything.

At the same time as she murmured, Esuka's head
exploded. Perhaps the power was restrained for
spectacle, parts of Esuka's head remained intact,
emphasizing the brutality even more.

I wanted to believe it was a fake. But as I stared
intently at the screen, all I could do was
acknowledge Esuka's death once again.
Unable to move, I remained collapsed.

When he joined the Resistance, he had been
thoroughly briefed that there might be times when
he would lose his comrades. Yet, the overly harsh
reality of his partner's death was more than
enough to shatter Shuu's heart.

Immediately after that, a report came in to the
Resistance headquarters that Shuu's base had been
attacked. There were no survivors. That was all
the report contained.
